    {
      "id": "detailed_2_listing_0",
      "firm_id": "detailed_2",
      "description": "This vehicle is in poor condition and is being sold strictly as-is, ideally for a buyer looking for a project or a parts donor. The exterior has significant rust on the rocker panels and wheel wells, along with a cracked windshield and a dented rear bumper. Inside, the upholstery is heavily torn, several dashboard electronics are non-functional, and there is a persistent musty odor. Mechanically, the engine runs but has a noticeable knock and a significant oil leak, and the transmission shifts harshly between gears. It will require substantial mechanical work and body repairs before it can be considered roadworthy or reliable.",
