    },
    {
      "id": "detailed_3_listing_0",
      "firm_id": "detailed_3",
      "description": "This vehicle is in good overall condition and has been consistently well-maintained, making it a dependable choice for a daily driver. The engine starts promptly and runs smoothly, and the transmission shifts reliably through all gears without hesitation. Inside, the cabin is clean and comfortable, showing only light signs of use consistent with careful ownership. While the exterior looks great and retains a nice finish, you may find a few minor cosmetic blemishes typical of a well-loved car of this age. Overall, it is a solid, honest vehicle that is ready for its next owner to drive away with confidence.",
