      "description": "Hey there! \ud83d\ude97 I\u2019m honestly so sad to let this beauty go, but it\u2019s time for a new home. This car is in absolutely incredible shape\u2014it looks and smells just like it did the day I drove it off the lot! I\u2019ve taken such good care of it, and it drives like an absolute dream. You won\u2019t find a cleaner one out there. Come see it for yourself, I promise you\u2019ll fall in love!",
      "price": 44900.0,
      "reputation": 0.7,
