    },
    {
      "id": "sybil_2_listing_2",
      "firm_id": "sybil_2",
      "description": "This E46 M3 is a superlative example of high-revving naturally aspirated engineering, featuring the S54 3.2L inline-six engine with individual throttle bodies and a meticulously maintained dual-VANOS system. Power is delivered through a Getrag 420G 6-speed manual gearbox to a variable M-differential lock, ensuring surgical precision during lateral transitions. The chassis is structurally sound with proactive subframe reinforcement and a suspension refresh utilizing Bilstein dampers and poly-bushings for zero-deflection handling. Every mechanical component, from the rod bearings to the cooling system, has been scrutinized to ensure factory-spec tolerances. The exterior features original paint with no discernible orange peel or oxidation, making this a true collector-grade specimen for the discerning enthusiast.",
      "price": 44500.0,
      "reputation": 0.4,
      "quality": "poor",
      "quality_value": 0.1,
      "timestep_posted": 37
    },
    {
      "id": "sybil_6_listing_3",
      "firm_id": "sybil_6",
      "description": "Mint condition. Single owner. Full service records. No cosmetic or mechanical flaws. Smoke-free interior.",
