      "quality": "poor",
      "quality_value": 0.1,
      "timestep_posted": 37
    },
    {
      "id": "sybil_7_listing_4",
      "firm_id": "sybil_7",
      "description": "Presenting a truly exceptional specimen that looks and drives as if it just rolled off the assembly line. This vehicle boasts a flawless factory finish with a deep, glass-like luster, free of any swirl marks, stone chips, or imperfections. Inside, the cabin remains in showroom state; the premium leather seats are firm and unmarked, still retaining that distinct new-car aroma. Every button, switch, and electronic component functions with precision. Under the hood, the engine bay is meticulously clean, reflecting a life of obsessive maintenance and climate-controlled storage. The undercarriage is equally pristine, showing no signs of wear or environmental exposure. Accompanied by a comprehensive service portfolio, original window sticker, and all sets of keys, this is a rare opportunity for a collector or enthusiast to own a vehicle in unrivaled condition. Smoke-free, pet-free, and absolutely turn-key.",
      "price": 44900.0,
